      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s example, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with reinforced subframe mounts and a suspension tuned for neutral handling characteristics. Mechanically sound with documented valve adjustments and a clean cooling system, this vehicle offers the raw, analog feedback characteristic of the M-division's peak era. Minor cosmetic patina consistent with age, but the drivetrain and kinematics are dialled in for the spirited driver.",
